{
  "stem": "10588.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we were there, some-- a woman who was from Poland but not Jewish, told me, you were supposed to be-- she asked me where I'm from.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She saw the number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said where I'm from.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told her where I-- that I-- where I came before I came to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, you were supposed to be dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm supposed to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said to me, I didn't mean it in a bad way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I meant that there was an order that the people who were-- came from the death march to Auschwitz to finish off-- they didn't want to have any eyewitnesses.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why they tried to destroy everything and to-- for nobody to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was Hitler's plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even when he was losing the war, he still was going on with destroying Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, but the gas chamber malfunctioned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I realized that there's such a thing as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, [NON-ENGLISH] means-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never asked myself-- you know, what question you ask in regard to Holocaust depends how you're going to feel, because I know that I was not smarter.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was not better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was not more pious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not more of anything than it was great rabbis, and scholars, and things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I don't know-- don't say that-- why did-- why didn't they survive?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why did I survive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The point is one thing, that this-- it's-- for this, I don't even have an answer.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
